Thanks for using the Yacht World App, the largest selection of luxury yachts available on your mobile device. Each update includes reliability and performance improvements. Also included in the latest update:


- Support for the Spanish language

- Ability to save search criteria

- Support for horizontal viewing of boat detail images

- Bug fixes
